itle">参见</h3>   <span>    <ul class="simplelist">     <li class="member"><span class="function">{@link imap_num_msg()} - Gets the number of messages in the current mailbox</span></li>     <li class="member"><span class="function">{@link imap_status()} - Returns status information on a mailbox</span></li>    </ul>   </span>  </div>  <div class="up"><a href="http://php.net/manual/zh/ref.imap.php">IMAP 函数</a></div></div>
