 style="color: #DD0000">"example.com"</span><span style="color: #007700">,&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #DD0000">"Hartmut&nbsp;Holzgraefe"</span><span style="color: #007700">);<br /></span><span style="color: #9876AA">?&gt;</span> </span> </span></div>     </div>      <div class="example-contents"><p>以上例程会输出：</p></div>     <div class="example-contents screen" style="background:black;padding-left:5px;"> <div class="cdata"><span> Hartmut Holzgraefe &lt;hartmut@example.com&gt; </span></div>     </div>    </div>   </span>  </div>  <div class="up"><a href="http://php.net/manual/zh/ref.imap.php">IMAP 函数</a></div></div>
