also">   <h3 class="title">参见</h3>   <span>    <ul class="simplelist">     <li class="member"><span class="function">{@link imap_8bit()} - Convert an 8bit string to a quoted-printable string</span></li>    </ul>   </span>  </div>  <div class="up"><a href="http://php.net/manual/zh/ref.imap.php">IMAP 函数</a></div></div>
