urns an UTF-8 encoded string.   </p>  </div>   <br></br><div style="BORDER-TOP: gray 1px dashed; OVERFLOW: hidden; HEIGHT: 1px"></div><div class="refsect1 seealso" id="refsect1-function.imap-utf8-seealso">   <h3 class="title">参见</h3>   <span>    <ul class="simplelist">     <li class="member"><span class="function">{@link imap_mime_header_decode()} - Decode MIME header elements</span></li>    </ul>   </span>  </div>  <div class="up"><a href="http://php.net/manual/zh/ref.imap.php">IMAP 函数</a></div></div>
